headline: Northrop Grumman Corporation (NOC) Eyes More Air Force Contracts For B-21 By Year End
summary: Northrop Grumman Corporation (NYSE:NOC) is among the 10 Largest Defense Stocks in 2025. During an earnings call with investors on October 21, CEO Kathy Warden said the defense firm was expecting more new U.S. Air Force (USAF) contracts for the B-21 program by the end of this year.
